### ============================================================
### PART 2: DYNAMIC DIFFICULTY ADJUSTMENT
### ============================================================
### AI automatically adjusts based on player performance
### - Win rate > 70% → Make AI harder
### - Win rate < 30% → Make AI easier
### - Win rate 30-70% → Keep same level
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Player Winning Too Much (80%) → Increase Difficulty
### Current: LOW → Recommended: MEDIUM
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-player/adjust-difficulty
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player_win_rate": 0.80,
    "current_level": "low"
}

### 2.2 Player Still Winning (75%) → Increase Again
### Current: MEDIUM → Recommended: HIGH
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-player/adjust-difficulty
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player_win_rate": 0.75,
    "current_level": "medium"
}

### 2.3 Balanced Game (50%) → Keep Same Level
### Current: MEDIUM → Recommended: MEDIUM
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-player/adjust-difficulty
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player_win_rate": 0.50,
    "current_level": "medium"
}

### 2.4 Player Losing Too Much (20%) → Decrease Difficulty
### Current: HIGH → Recommended: MEDIUM
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-player/adjust-difficulty
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player_win_rate": 0.20,
    "current_level": "high"
}

### 2.5 Player Still Losing (25%) → Decrease Again
### Current: MEDIUM → Recommended: LOW
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-player/adjust-difficulty
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "player_win_rate": 0.25,
    "current_level": "medium"
}

